Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.24,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:10.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて抱きしめてみるのは罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:17.64,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:23.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘆いても夢は唄わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:29.23,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此所で叫んだよ「答えは誰が持ってるの？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.70,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}俯いたままじゃ気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:39.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君の瞳の中　未来を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:45.19,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もしも奇跡が今を指すなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.91,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}にじむ涙ぬぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.45,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前を向いて歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:02:00.99,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}こんな苦しさで何も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:06.09,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:14.12,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて彼方へ　情熱は罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:21.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.24,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:10.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃燒的胸懷抱緊你 這不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:17.64,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:23.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出夢想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:29.23,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底誰能給我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:33.70,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抬起頭來才能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:39.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有著我尋覓已久的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:45.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如果奇跡指向這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.91,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.45,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向前大步前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:55.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:02:00.99,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在如此的煉獄中會迷失前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:06.09,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃盡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:14.12,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}化為一道烈焰逝向彼方 這渾身的炙熱不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:21.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驅散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:16.23,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:24.17,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:33.86,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:42.76,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:51.32,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:23:02.25,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:16.23,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的孤獨 一時間的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:24.17,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為我帶來的瑰寶 一樣樣都令人愛不釋手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:33.86,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕兩人之間的距離觸手可及 可無形之壁註定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:42.76,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心宛如明月 陰晴圓缺不斷變幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:51.32,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定依舊無法實現 眼淚仍然不願乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:23:02.25,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把你給的瑰寶 緊擁懷中驀然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小此木 意外地有料啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？沒那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 仔細這麼一看還真是..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像庚同學這樣苗條型的才出挑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庚同學 我可以摸摸看妳的腿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然妳也可以摸摸看我的胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便附贈一下臀部也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝..牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸摸看妳的腿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪之四 拂曉少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 開始舉行靈異調查部暑假強化合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然之間要搞合宿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這..這個嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的夏夜出現一兩個靈異現象是理所當然的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這都不去進行調查 那還算什麼靈異調查部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是晚上要住在學校裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了嗎？新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我倒沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳沒關係吧 庚同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前妳也一個人就哭了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是不太擅長應付這種嚇人的東西吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我說過那是不可抗力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是天黑腳陂動彈不得而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和新谷同學一起進行合宿真是令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是靈異調查部的強化合宿到底是要強化什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是關於怪談的真相嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是夕子學姐嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是這個學園最有名的怪談呢 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 說得對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個了不起的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從哪裡入手調查？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間可是多得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人期待呢 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是舊值夜室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們睡覺的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 榻榻米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學校方面居然能點頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明是個非正式的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦 只要拜託奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數的問題都可以解決啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡茶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到值夜一定要麵包和茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從水龍頭裏流出了血！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 新谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈異現象這麼快就出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是太久不用水管生銹了而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要多放一會水就會變乾淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是靈異現象感覺有點遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感覺的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有值夜日記耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好舊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個年頭的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲擊門板的聲音又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚 咚咚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門板被強烈的敲擊著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為有人來而開門一看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而門前一定是空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果不開門一直放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼敲擊門板的聲音會變得愈見強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個學校有著不屬於這個世界的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值夜室的怪談？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚真是令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好..好哇 從日落了就開始認真調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們把夏夜的校舍調查個水落石出吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..為什麼是游泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包場啊包場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要感謝庚同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不..我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為靈異現象的調查要晚上才正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天還是養精蓄銳一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所..所以我穿了件新泳衣來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎 新谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？有這麼不合身嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:07.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！好痛..痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！我看上去是如此地痛心疾首嗎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！好痛..請別這樣.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 別這樣穿比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太華麗了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小此木同學 妳誤會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 很合身啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情反而更顯殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我去重新換過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 小此木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼啊 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是被她誤會了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 新谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷同學 球過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們上吧 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這裡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為值夜室的幽靈說不定會出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按恐怖電影的設定單獨行動的人會最先碰到靈異現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可第一個犧牲的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像..氣氛越來越像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然..不這樣的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還挺意外的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為庚同學會不太喜歡合宿之類的活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧 我要尋找幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈的話不是有一個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學園裏說不定有其他的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頭一回見到她的時候 夕子也是和現在一樣的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我也不認為夕子是惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看見了 影子..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它出現在日沒之後的校舍中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被憤怒和憎恨扭曲的惡靈之影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到它之後我就錯以為夕子露出了真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在那以後 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼中的夕子開始變成那副陰森恐怖的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是因為我內心的主觀因素所致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子並非就是那個惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我所看到的那個陰森恐怖的樣子到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學園裏確實存在著惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前因為孤身一人所以只能一味逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在..有了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 新谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪裡去了 新谷？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一是個笨蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多天一直把我撇在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..因為一直是暑假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為終於把你盼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你卻只和大家玩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了我的泳衣也毫無表示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只有貞一了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過霧江同學也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也能看見夕子學姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看得見 她也不肯接觸我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們好久沒觸碰到彼此了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過..平時都是我主動所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒？夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且第一次是貞一主動來觸摸我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你想要的..就算是第一次觸摸到的地方也..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就手吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？機會是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就摸手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由貞一來握住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然讓妳變成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人突然消失了 嚇了我一跳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧..霧江同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小此木同學不會睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲門叫醒她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什..什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成..是值夜室的幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是過去的日記上記載的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到晚上 不屬於這個世界的東西會巡遊此地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷 從外面的窗戶進去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小此木同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才值夜室的幽靈出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚咚咚敲個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我這個單獨行動者差點就成了第一個犧牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值夜室的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩紙牌吧紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈似乎不喜歡到氣氛活躍的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 玩抽鬼牌行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼要發四人份的牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然啦 因為有四個人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加上新谷加上小此木加上..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啊！！房間裏不止三人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈是睡不著的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是值夜日記嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前啊 我經常來這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了冬天很冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間有暖爐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人可以看見夕子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 因為敲門的話會以為外面有人而開門嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就趁機進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是重覆幾次之後 就沒有人為我開門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打開門也沒人在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後光是敲門就會使大家害怕起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這裡記載的事情都是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在才想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了老掉牙的往事就想睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎團這種東西一旦解開就失去了特殊之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶一旦回憶起來也盡是些平凡瑣事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那種東西而要破壞現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒石？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕..夕子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈不是睡不著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可以陪人入睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這麼晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日沒之後意外地涼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊 因為這個學校是建在山上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算夏天也有點涼涼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人 偷跑出去想要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼？怎麼幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子當然抵擋不住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底差在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是想一想就能變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮..要留長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一 你知道詛咒石嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒石？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那顆石頭上刻上怨恨的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能降下詛咒並殺死那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果找到的那個石頭上刻著自己的名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會因詛咒而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學園裏似乎有這種石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊校舍的內院中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這個學校的老師找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個老師遭到了石頭的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃避石頭的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老師辭了職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件全記載在了這個日記上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒石的怪談..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要調查看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上再說嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 死路？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是上得去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過之後因為改建而被封死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以從那邊跳到隔壁的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐 危險 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁校舍的屋頂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 夕子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要從哪裡過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只是單純的死路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跑過來看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要從窗戶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只能從窗戶進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是舊校舍的內院哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被長廊所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按值夜日記記載
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的某處有詛咒石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是那塊石頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個..全部是人名？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面刻上名字就能殺死對方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而發現石頭上面刻著自己的名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會因詛咒而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是..詛咒石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒石上..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新谷貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被詛咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做出這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦..這樣下去的話我會被咒殺而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是為了這種惡作劇才把我叫醒的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 感覺死得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒這種東西 並不存在於現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過..能讓人覺得不寒而栗 這本身可能就是詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞一也來游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但..但是 現在沒穿泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說值夜日記的老師遭到了詛咒一定也只是人的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他暗暗知道誰會詛咒他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種小事就辭職了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人無法發現自己對事物的相信與否根本無從掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意間相信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的力量就會在此萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 雖然詛咒石真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那是藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開不開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜的散步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓貞一看一看這個學園的另一番面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天色越來越淺..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻總讓人覺得夜明時分似乎永遠不會來臨的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段美好的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議呢 之前我想都沒想過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚明明總是這麼轉瞬而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子學姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是因為貞一發現了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 貞一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿衣鏡中..顯出的美艷之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忌避所產生的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深愛著你的我 
